metadata.name: Five Head #7393
metadata.description: The Five Head Circle is an NFT collection consisting of 10000 unique digital Five Heads living on the Ethereum blockchain. Holders of a Five Head can decide which of four factions they want to belong to. Depending on the chosen faction, which can only be set once, the background of the NFT changes automatically. The membership brings different character traits and virtues to which the members should adhere. Learn more at fiveheadcircle.com.
